com.geocent.geocentlabs.wps.exportscene.ppio

Class ColladaScenePPIO

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.geoserver.wps.ppio.ProcessParameterIO
      • org.geoserver.wps.ppio.ComplexPPIO
        • org.geoserver.wps.ppio.XMLPPIO
          • com.geocent.geocentlabs.wps.exportscene.ppio.ColladaScenePPIO

  • public class ColladaScenePPIO
extends org.geoserver.wps.ppio.XMLPPIO
    This class binds the conversion of the computed terrain mesh to the "model/vnd.collada+xml" mimeType attribute of the wps:RawDataOutput for the implemented WPS. The output is a very minimal COLLADA asset file conforming to the 1.4.1 version of the specification.
    Author:
    Joshua Penton
